Goodnight! 😍 This home is located at 13106 S Riverbendview Cove in Riverton, Utah and is situated on an acre of land.

It was built in 2008 and features approximately 13,296 square feet of living space with 6 bedrooms, 10 bathrooms, 2-story foyer with staircase, elevator, formal living & dining rooms, 2-story great room with 2nd staircase, gourmet kitchen, breakfast room, office, game/rec room with wet bar, home theater, indoor basketball court, playroom with ball pit, 10-car detached garage with additional living space and more.

Outdoor features include balconies/patios, kitchen/BBQ, fire pit and a swimming pool with spa.

🌍 13106 S Riverbendview Cove, Riverton, Utah 🏠 13,296 Square Feet 🛏 6 Bedrooms 🛁 10 Bathrooms 💰 $5,900,000

Good morning! 😍 This newly built stone & brick home is located at 4725 Northside Drive in Sandy Springs, Georgia and is situated on over 6.5 acres of land.

It features approximately 15,000 square feet of living space with 7 bedrooms, 9 full and 3 half bathrooms, foyer with staircase, formal living room, gourmet kitchen, breakfast room, family room, office, game room/bowling alley with wet bar, wine cellar, home theater, gym, indoor lap pool, indoor basketball court, 6-car garage and an attached pool house complete with living room & 2nd kitchen.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, motor court, terraces, kitchen/BBQ, fireplace and an infinity pool with spa.

🌍 4725 Northside Drive, Sandy Springs, Georgia 🏠 15,000 Square Feet 🛏 7 Bedrooms 🛁 12 Bathrooms 💰 $9,800,000

Goodnight! 😍 This is the home that professional poker player and social media playboy Dan Bilzerian was renting in California for $200,000/month.

The modern mega mansion is located at 10979 Chalon Road in the Bel Air neighborhood of Los Angeles. The owner decided it was time to put it back on the market after receiving lots of interest in the home. It was last listed at $67,500,000.

Built in 2017, it features approximately 31,000 square feet of living space with 12 bedrooms, 19 full and 6 half bathrooms, multiple staircases, elevator, multiple living & dining rooms, gourmet kitchen, 5 wet bars, wine cellar, 40+ seat home theater, 2-lane bowling alley, salon/spa, 14-car garage and much more. There is also a guard house with kitchen and bathroom.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, motor court, 40,000 square feet of outdoor living space, balconies, water & fire features, 70′ infinity pool, spa, cabana, BBQ, tennis court and a putting green.
